title: Desktop Support Technician
description: Washington State Ferries (WSF) currently has a special opportunity for an ambitious IT professional who is enthusiastic, hardworking and is looking to join a dynamic IT Desktop Support team.As a member of the IT support team, the Information Technology Support Specialist 4 position provides tech support to a proud organization that helps supports the livelihood and economic success of communities in the Puget Sound and beyond.

title: Corporate IT Support Specialist II
description: Under limited supervision, administers all aspects of an advanced, distributed computer system supporting a specified functional area of operations. Plans and coordinates system utilization. Performs systems and applications programming to produce a variety of innovative solutions to complex problems. Performs installation, maintenance, training, and user support, as required; plans and coordinates projects to meet future needs. Analyzes user requirements, procedures, and problems to automate processing or to improve existing computer system by performing the following duties.

title: Information Technology Trainee
description: Work for an industry leader while learning cutting edge technology. Eagle Creek Software Services, a rapidly growing Software Services company, is currently seeking entry level software consultants for our Technology Center in Vermillion, South Dakota (relocation assistance available). At the technology center you will receive hands-on training to work toward becoming an IT consultant, engaged on software implementations from project initiation to final customer roll out.

title: Store Graphic Artist/Signmaker
description: Design and create graphics for promotions, store literature, and signage, including computer generated and hand drawn flyers, shelf signs, chalkboards, and the store calendar.

title: Graphic Designer
description: Teramind is looking for an experienced Graphics Designer who's familiar with designing multiple facets of visual concepts. This position reports to the Head of Marketing and will be responsible for creating and maintaining Teramind's graphic assets and webpage designs. The ideal candidate has experience with designing for technology companies' websites, blogs, and brochures.

title: IT Specialist (CUSTSPT/INFOSEC)

We take great pride in serving the men and women who serve America, and invite goal-oriented people like you to challenge yourself while providing a service to our nation.
